## ğŸ§© Architecture
![Architecture](architecture.png)

**Flow Summary:**
1. Developers push code to GitHub â†’ triggers Jenkins pipeline.  
2. Jenkins builds app, runs SonarQube scan, creates Docker image.  
3. Terraform provisions infra â†’ EKS, EC2, RDS, IAM, S3.  
4. Jenkins deploys app to EKS â†’ updates service via rolling strategy.  
5. Prometheus & Grafana monitor app metrics and alert on anomalies.

